data.description:
4 true Bedrooms and 2 bath, with an extra room to turn into whatever you want, we used it as a walk in closet, shelves and clothing pipes will stay, this room does not have central air and is not figured into the square footage of the house. 
All Newer Kitchen with Island, New kitchen appliance purchased in oct 2022 . New Master Suite Addition with Tiled Shower. There is a Bonus Room. 1,764 Square Feet Heated Living Space. Tiled Flooring, Fans.  New roof with 50 year warranty completed by RoofBar with hurricane straps done in Sept. 2020, Electrical panel along with solar panels and system installed in Nov 2020 by solarbear, new 20 seer RUUD a/c system installed in Dec 2020,Water heater 2017. Safe touch security system installed and able to transfer service, equipment stays here.  New 8’ X 12’ wood building in backyard.  Wood poles from deck in place for hammocks in back yard. No HOA.  BONUS ROOM THAT IS CURRENTLY SET UP AS A WALK IN CLOSET AND IS SPACE THAT NEEDS CENTRAL AC DROPPED AND WOULD ADD TO THE VALUE AND ADDITIONAL SQUARE FOOTAGE OF THE HOME. 

appliance information: glass top stove is a LG smart stove with air fry feature and connects to app on phone as well the LG above the stove microwave.
